    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. Mechanically, it is very sound; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts precisely, and it handles beautifully on both city streets and highways. The interior is exceptionally clean, featuring comfortable seating with only minor signs of use, and all electronic features and climate controls are fully functional. While the exterior paint still holds a nice shine, there are a few small stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Overall, this is a reliable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
