    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it's in pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that's basically brand new, this is definitely the one. I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
