      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the E46 chassis. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension geometry is sharpened by Bilstein PSS10 coilovers. The exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible imperfections, while the interior showcases untouched Nappa leather. This is a turnkey, investment-grade driver\u2019s car with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
