    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-ready condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint retains its original factory depth and luster, completely free from swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the original alloy wheels are pristine, devoid of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the precision climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, documented service history showing proactive maintenance that exceeds factory requirements. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage reflects the car's pampered life on dry roads only. This is a collector-grade vehicle that drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Sale includes all original keys, stamped service books, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover.",
